@Access_Token = 在这里粘贴通过 OIDC 获取的 access_token
@Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5100

@PrivateAttachmentId = <私有附件的ID>
@AccessToken = <从创建令牌响应中复制 token>
@TokenToRevoke = <要撤销的 token>
@TargetUserId = 20001

### 为附件创建临时访问令牌
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Attachment/CreateAccessToken
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "attachmentId": {{PrivateAttachmentId}},
  "validHours": 24,
  "maxAccessCount": 10,
  "authorizedUserId": null,
  "authorizedIp": null
}

### 使用令牌下载文件
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Attachment/DownloadByToken?token={{AccessToken}}

### 创建限制访问次数的令牌
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Attachment/CreateAccessToken
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "attachmentId": {{PrivateAttachmentId}},
  "validHours": 1,
  "maxAccessCount": 1,
  "authorizedUserId": null,
  "authorizedIp": null
}

### 创建限制用户的令牌
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Attachment/CreateAccessToken
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "attachmentId": {{PrivateAttachmentId}},
  "validHours": 24,
  "maxAccessCount": 0,
  "authorizedUserId": {{TargetUserId}},
  "authorizedIp": null
}

### 创建限制 IP 的令牌
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Attachment/CreateAccessToken
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "attachmentId": {{PrivateAttachmentId}},
  "validHours": 24,
  "maxAccessCount": 0,
  "authorizedUserId": null,
  "authorizedIp": "192.168.1.100"
}

### 撤销访问令牌
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Attachment/RevokeAccessToken
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

"{{TokenToRevoke}}"

### 获取附件的所有令牌
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Attachment/GetAttachmentTokens?attachmentId={{PrivateAttachmentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 测试过期令牌
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Attachment/CreateAccessToken
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "attachmentId": {{PrivateAttachmentId}},
  "validHours": 0.0003,
  "maxAccessCount": 0,
  "authorizedUserId": null,
  "authorizedIp": null
}

### 访问过期令牌（预期 403）
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Attachment/DownloadByToken?token=<过期的token>

### 测试访问次数限制：第 1 次
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Attachment/DownloadByToken?token=<token>

### 测试访问次数限制：第 2 次
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Attachment/DownloadByToken?token=<token>

### 测试访问次数限制：第 3 次（预期 403）
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Attachment/DownloadByToken?token=<token>

### 使用无效令牌（预期 403）
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Attachment/DownloadByToken?token=invalid-token-12345
